Package evaluation.networkperformance

Class Summary
ComplexEnrichment Contains one static method to calculate the complex enrichment score of a network with respect to a complex set.
ROC Contains static methods to calculate ROC curves for protein networks.
ROCCurve An immutable list of ROC points, result of a ROC curve calculation
ROCCurveHandler Contains static functions for writing ROC curves to files and creating actual plots from the ROC curves using Gnuplot or the JFreeChart library.
ROCPoint One single point in a ROC curve consisting of a true positive rate and a false positive rate value.
